Translating Business needs into Business Insights ;
Doing business and data analysis that support the business ;
Preparing data for analysis;
Developing reports using Tableau ;
Training users ;
Documentation of the learnings and methods applied ;
M aintaining the dashboards ;
Combining the Efficiency in Business Intelligence with Creativity in Business Analytics .
