4+ years of experience as data analyst ;
3+ years of experience with Tableau andSQL is a must ( experience with launching tableau for the first time in an organization is a plus);
Stakeholder management and good communication skills ;
AWS experience is good to have ;
Statistical knowledge and data modelling is required;
