As a Seismic Navigation Data Processor, you assist in all aspects of our seismic navigation requirements and deliverables, including QC, validating, and processing of seismic survey navigation sets. You assist project teams in setting up and verifying Starfix settings for seismic operations. In this varied role you provide support to operations in analysis and trouble shooting and assist the Seismic Navigation Supervisor as required.
