You assist online surveyors in Starfix NG setup to ensure correct format and standard of deliverables are being realised;
You are involved in Starfix configuration, analyse first line QC reports and provide feedback to the vessel;
You assist in processing navigation data required in the production of project deliverables and in processing large data volumes to meet project requirements;
